      <prefercite id="aspace_24031d4c4805ecd14c0eda7c2041bc4b">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Yale School of Drama Records of the Search Committee for the Dean (RU 731). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_a33fbb1791b1bd92fa041c45e10b6dc2">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by subject.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_e9393e70a119781887bc43e5647b36cc">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of correspondence, recommendations, letters, newspaper clippings, printed materials, applications, and nominations documenting the 1978 search committee for a dean of the Yale School of Drama.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_66fcb86d029426c4b0a1ded436b1264e">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>Some records in this finding aid have been redacted, as they include student names, donor names, and other restricted data. These records will not appear in the published finding aid.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
